summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical underground distribution easements over portions of Maywood Acre Tracts; Northeast 1/4 of Section 19, Township 23 North, Range 4 East; Northwest 1/4 of Section 8, Township 26 North, Range 4 East; Northlake Addition; Southeast 1/4 of Section 18, Township 26 North, Range 4 East; and Northwest 1/4 of Section 3, Township 23 North, Range 4 East.
